def calculate_uptime(start_time):
    """Calcular uptime desde inicio"""
    delta = datetime.now() - start_time
    hours = int(delta.total_seconds() // 3600)
    minutes = int((delta.total_seconds() % 3600) // 60)
    return f"{hours}h {minutes}m"
